snippet.title: AVGN 1 & 2 Deluxe - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
The 'Nerd is back with an HD upgrade, more difficulty options, re balanced challenges, some new surprises & an all-new 3rd chapter to bring the entire package together!

AVGN Deluxe is available now!
https://AVGNgame.com

Find AVGN I & II Deluxe and other games published by Screenwave Media at http://games.screenwavemedia.com
